sec.p:
Participants are randomised to one of three treatment groups in a ratio of 1:1:1 as follows:
Topical corticosteroid ointment plus dummy NB-UVB light (corticosteroid only);
Vehicle ointment plus NB-UVB light (light therapy only);
Topical corticosteroid ointment plus NB-UVB light (combination therapy).
